metadata.name: Voice of God
metadata.description:
"Father, did you speak to god?"
The Father answered with a nod.
"Will you tell me what he said?"
The Father simply shook his head.
"Father, please, relay His word?"
Then something in the Father stirred.
But when the Father tried to speak,
What came out was an awful shriek.
Then, in a blink, and blinding light,
The Father vanished; out of sight.
